name: My Many Faces #3
description:
Minted at Tezos 402nd cycle.

"It's just like the question: 'why the world be otherwise?'. It's all used up. All that beauty we had."

This series of my first work is created through Generative Adversarial Network or GAN. I put in 1000 pictures of mask and create a million string of new pictures. This work will be minted every Tezos cycle and with the help of a simple algorithm, only the selected one will formed an appearance.
